### Properties

 - `$config`
   - `$config->type` → Return an empty string on home page, `page` on item page and `pages` on index page. Default is `404`.
   - `$config->state` → Return the current page state. Default is `page`.

### Hooks

 - `elevator.pager` → Will affect the HTML output of the page’s pagination.